<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">　<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">            </span>《古城新貌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                          　 　 　   　</span>刘明源曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></span></p>
