<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                       《战马奔腾》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                       </span>陈耀星曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                         演奏：李福华（国家一级演员）</span></p>
